description:
=-- Storyline --=

After "hooking up" with a series of guys at a house party, 
April is the talk of her high school. Her best friend Michelle, 
envious of all of April's attention, decides to try and follow 
in her footsteps and become more sexually forward. At the same 
time, their mutual friend Caroline has become so infatuated with 
her older boyfriend Ryan that she doesn't realize he's just 
using her. All the while, John, spends the week informing his 
two best friends, Colin (April's repressed and confused brother) 
and Tyler (the subject of Michelle's crush), about obscure sexual 
urban legends he reads about online, that just somehow end up 
managing to come true. Throw in the naive principal Dr. Jordan, 
who also happens to be Michelle's father, and Mr. Kimbal, a 
chemistry teacher trying desperately to dodge repeated seduction 
attempts from his students.


=-- Cast --=

Corey Feldman ... Ryan
Brian O'Halloran ... Dr. Jordan
Bronson Pinchot ... Mr. Kimbal
